Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  暑假期間要注意身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個暑假都和小杏見不到面  阿土卻還這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是因為有這麼長的假期才高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了阿土  今年夏天你要回老家去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不  沒打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  要不要趁著暑假去看看我和阿土從小長大的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和阿土從小長大的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也邀上小柊和小梅她們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？  那阿土呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼連我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  各位要一起去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們暑假期間要到媽媽和阿土從小長大的地方去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本老師也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在說什麼呢  小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本老師你意向如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  不會給你們添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有那回事呢  對吧阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊  一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也邀了小柊和小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那這樣的話也算上我一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照了  櫻小姐  土田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏也要多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}花丸暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土  這好像蜜月旅行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  所謂的蜜月旅行指的是新婚夫婦兩個人單獨去旅行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要是有像這樣的蜜月旅行也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  山本老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  像這樣熱熱鬧鬧的也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說得也是  像這樣集體出遊的蜜月旅行也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊  今天的阿土表現得可真積極
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土的新娘都夠開後宮了  你可真受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為說是蜜月旅行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在座的各位就都是阿土的新娘了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  那山本老師也是囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  是這樣嗎  我也是啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅也是新娘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重婚在法律上可是不允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家一起嫁給土田老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就算是這樣  最深愛阿土的還是小杏我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你說什麼呢學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這簡直就是九星連珠一般的罕見現象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  請不要在車廂裡喧嘩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  土田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了小杏  我也跟著鬧起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我個人是一點也不介意啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土還是一點也沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是什麼意思啊  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  土田老師和櫻小姐是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  阿土他啊  因為喜歡我所以一直黏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  才沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡說什麼呢學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻學姐小時候是孩子王  總是拽著我到處跑來跑去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿過這條隧道就到我和阿土的家鄉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土就是在這種地方長大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說「這種地方」也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微走一點路就有便利店的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李交給我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:32.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來都是上坡路  孩子們就交給你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東北雨蛙生活在地勢平緩的森林或草原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時在較矮的樹上或者草叢中活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  阿土很體貼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦  學姐的行李也給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真是好久都沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位遠道而來辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨  好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面  阿姨  我是小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是柊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你啦  阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點程度就趴下的話是當不了幼稚園老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  全都讓你拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  這點小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敝姓山本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  五月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  五月妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是青蛙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是疣蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子來了這麼多人真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別客氣  人多熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還在國外吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  在那邊享清福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏是櫻姐的女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  我真沒想到你會帶這麼個姑娘回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的小子怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他一直對我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裡來的路上都是他幫我扛著行李
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼聘禮要怎麼弄？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小柊  聘禮是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的聘禮  就是指為了確定婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙方家人互贈金錢財物的風俗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「婚約」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是約定結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在說什麼呢媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和山本老師不是那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的那是怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  山本老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記告訴您了  其實我是土田老師的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是想能幫著照顧一下孩子們  就請他們帶我一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然時日不長  還是要請您多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  似乎讓阿姨誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  我還以為這下能早點抱上孫子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土是要對小杏送聘禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小杏要當直純的新娘子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後就請讓我叫您媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  直純是指阿土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提漢字是這樣寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以後我也得叫阿土「直純」了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏你真的很喜歡土田老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點沒錯  嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還是叫阿土就夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土看起來沒精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管他  阿土還正值青春年少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天大家一起去後山的那條河那裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後山的河？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿土充滿回憶的地方…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡水魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涼涼的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土也來一起游嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過像這樣坐在一邊看著山本老師的泳裝打扮偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真夠邪惡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  我有笑得那麼明顯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐  這次旅行你為什麼把山本老師都一起叫來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？  當然是為了聲援阿土你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心意我很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是小杏知道了會生你的氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是嗎  可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本沒考慮過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做事還是那麼奔放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前經常和阿土一起到這裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論發生了什麼事情都在這裡談心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  你沒去約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是櫻學姐擅自替我決定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？你不是說過喜歡她的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒那個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說了  約會什麼的不應該是別人代為決定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要再這麼說  小心一輩子交不上女朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…我對學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你又怎麼樣  你也沒有男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的  最近交上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說從今往後我和他就是情侶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？你的班主任？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是大叔了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太沒禮貌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是不懂呀  這就叫成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你們可是老師和學生的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是不會有結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要和他交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想為了他活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你那一臉呆樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土你也快點交個女朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則你一個人怎麼過得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是說  我能和山本老師一起旅行都是多虧了櫻學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻學姐真的和自己的老師交往  結婚  還當了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻從學生時代開始就沒任何長進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到頭來還是什麼都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  這些地方還能和以前一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前一樣可不行  我也是會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  阿土！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？五月  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的  哥哥  我前段時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小柊她抓到了好大的一隻螳螂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  等會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的螳螂長得很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.21,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小柊真厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很強…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花丸夏祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些全都是五月做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還做了義大利薯丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縣內舉辦的廚藝大賽上  我們社團做這個得了第二名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？你參加料理社團啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家吃到這些以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能對哥哥保密不要說是我做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓他吃的時候給他一個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個糯糯的  真的很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  今天的飯菜是山本老師做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是我做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那難道說是媽媽做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這樣的話  就是櫻學姐了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是家庭主婦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我可做不了這麼精緻的飯菜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  這裡還有其他很擅長做菜的女孩子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是小杏你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你這個…大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起  五月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也不用那麼生氣嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是阿土你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  阿土你太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是你做的  那一開始就說清楚不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你個大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後啊…阿土就一直盯著那個穿著可愛裙子的姐姐看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  那種事情就不要再抖落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直純你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  沒關係  你繼續說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  阿土上次在便利店裡蹭小黃本看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  你是不是誤會什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你自作自受啊  直純
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  哥哥真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土在小杏爬到樹上下不來的時候來救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏當時從樹上摔下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土「呀」地一聲奮勇撲上來保護了小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅當時害怕得都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就「只有」那一次最帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那一次嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直純你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從被阿土緊緊抱在懷裡的那時候起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏眼裡除了阿土已經容不下別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來小杏在游泳池裡被鯊魚襲擊的時候也是阿土來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  那是你編的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯊魚是我扮的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過救了差點從樹上摔下來的小杏的那一回是確有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥終究還是在盡責地當老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對  哥哥他是在我看不到的地方努力著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡阿土了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在我背上很熱的  快下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒機會讓他看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我在這裡等你  不用著急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏  你還醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你還生阿土的氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在雖然是這副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以前的哥哥跟現在可是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  阿土以前是什麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…怎麼說呢…是個很貼心的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都黏著哥哥跟他玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不說出口  他也總能明白我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是有了煩惱  他也馬上就能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿土現在也是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  阿土很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家都很喜歡阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杏這麼說的話  應該是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  明天就是夏日祭典了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧  穿上浴衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了  還能看到煙火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  真的嗎  煙火！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在開始祭典以前  要先跟神明打招呼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小梅也要去打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也去  希望更多的人能注重環保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家都健健康康的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  希望哥哥能常回家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能快點跟阿土發展成男女關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到那邊去吧  小杏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿莉控？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  那邊有神轎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  別把小杏她們扔下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅小柊一起手拉手過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱抱我！阿土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小梅和小柊就和老師我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山本老師一起來真是幫了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是我一直給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫上忙我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你在那裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心別走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  丟下你一個人在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不會丟下你了  別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有賣五月喜歡喝的甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起去喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你怎麼知道我在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得小時候你迷路那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是一個人躲在這裡哭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚真對不起  你做的菜實在太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  真的有那麼好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  簡直像是專業廚師做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  我們的社團做那道菜在廚藝大賽上得獎了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得獎？  很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有獎狀呢  回頭給你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  那可得看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋原本是江戶時代有名的煙火製造老字號…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:31.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暑假二三事）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  故鄉就是好哇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是阿土好像稍微有點鬱悶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來有請好友三人組  拜託你們了  能行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週是魚店老闆和小杏的情敵登場的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:44.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花丸魚老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}花丸情敵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:09.01,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らは真っ黒いネコ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:16.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,何か　楽しい事　ないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:24.54,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,駆け抜ける。都会を。ニャオ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:31.21,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,今はまだ宵の口だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:40.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,あの角に光るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:48.30,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,ボスネコとその仲間の目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:55.85,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,気づかれない様にね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:03.35,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,いつものジャズクラブに向かうんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,眠らない都会に。ニャオ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:16.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆっくりスイング　ゆだねてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,またたびをなめたら　すぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:26.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah　心地良くなっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:16.44,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是黑色的貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:24.54,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡有樂子可以找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:31.21,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭在都市中喵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:40.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是夜色初上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:48.30,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊街角閃爍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:55.85,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,是貓老大和他手下的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:03.35,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不被他們發現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,就往常去的爵士俱樂部的方向去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:16.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,在無眠的都市中喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,沉浸在爵士樂的跳躍節奏中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:26.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,只要舔到那美味的木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:26.88,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　那是多麼的愜意啊
